WEBVTT

00:00:28.707 --> 00:00:31.665
local police departments 
to gather vast quantities

00:00:31.665 --> 00:00:35.232
of sensitive information
about each and every one of us

00:00:35.232 --> 00:00:39.284
in a way that was
never previously possible.

00:00:39.284 --> 00:00:42.760
Location information can 
be very sensitive.

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:45.391
If you drive your car around
the United States,

00:00:45.391 --> 00:00:47.314
it can reveal if you go 
to a therapist,

00:00:47.314 --> 00:00:49.782
attend an Alcoholics Anonymous meeting,

00:00:49.782 --> 00:00:52.603
if you go to church 
or if you don't go to church.

00:00:52.603 --> 00:00:54.329
And when that 
information about you

00:00:54.329 --> 00:00:57.824
is combined with the same information
about everyone else,

00:00:57.824 --> 00:01:00.398
the government can gain 
